	</div>
</section>
{{!-- food section end --}}

{{!-- cages section start --}}
<section class="section" id="toys">
	<div class="hero is-primary products-header">
		<div class="hero-body is-bold">
			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="title">
					Toys
				</h1>
				<h2 class="subtitle">
					Keep your bird entertained while you're away with our wide selection of bird-safe toys.
				</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="container notification">
		<div class="content">
			<p>Providing toys are an essential part of a parrot’s mental health.</p>
			<p>We design our own unique acrylic and wood toys. We also carry a large selection of other toy companies parrot toys.</p>
			<p>Parrots need toys for destruction, forging and interaction to stimulate their intelligence and keep them entertained. Keep in mind parrots have the intelligence of a five year old child. Parrots love to play and interact with toys and people.</p>
			<p>Recommendations: 4 to 5 toys per cage, play gym top cages should have 1 to 2 additional toys.</p>
			<p>Change at least one toy every week to avoid boredom.</p>
			<p>Parrots that are happy, active and entertained exhibit few or no behavioral problems.</p>
			<p>Note: All acrylic toys are dishwasher safe.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
{{!-- cages section end --}}